Procedura di rendering (1 per frame)

- setOrthoProj
- useShader:
	- glUseProgram
	- glEnableVertexAttribArray
	- glActiveTexture
	- glUniform1i
- glClearDepth
- glClear
- glClearColor
- render
	- glBindVertexArray
	- glBindTexture
	- glDrawArrays
	- glBindVertexArray(0)
- unuseShader:
	- glUseProgram(0)
	- glDisableVertexAttribArray
	- glBindTexture(0)
- swapWindow

Vecchia procedura di rendering (1 per frame)

useShader:
	- glUseProgram
	- glEnableVertexAttribArray
	- glActiveTexture
	- glUniform1i
- setOrthoProj
- glClearDepth
- glClearDepth
- glClearColor
- render
	- glBindVertexArray
	- glBindTexture
	- glDrawArrays
	- glBindVertexArray
- swapWindow
- unuseShader:
	- glUseProgram(0)
	- glDisableVertexAttribArray
	- glBindTexture(0)
